headline: Davis Global Fund 2025 Semi-Annual Review
summary: Davis Global Fund posted a strong return of +14.12% in the first six months of 2025, outperforming its MSCI ACWI (All Country World Index) benchmark. Read more here.

headline: Davis International Fund 2025 Semi-Annual Review
summary: Davis International Fund posted a strong return of +16.32% in the first six months of 2025, though this was below the performance of the MSCI ACWI (All Country World Index) ex US benchmark.
